<NEW>

As VICE GRIP is placed in a CR chamber by INFERNO, WASPINATOR came
straggling in as well, his shoulder blackened from the zap he had
received from an annoyed HYDRAS during the battle.

The rest of the Predacons were also making their way back towards the
downed ship that was doubling now as HYDRAS' base. The ship was still
in excellent repairs, everything powered and ready to go, it being
able to to everything but fly.

SKY SHADOW came to meet HYDRAS as he came to the entrance. "Greetings
sir." he said in overly docile tones. "It is good to see you have
returned so quickly and with new soldiers." It is obvious he had
already seen VICE GRIP as he was brought in and he looked over at
DINOBOT as well. "Good . good."

There was a pause from SKY SHADOW, "Where is Taratulus? I thought he
went out with you, but I do not see him with you Lord Hydras?" There
was a brief smile from SKY SHADOW, one that was immediately covered by
a look of (false?) sorrow. "He wasn't damaged out in battle was he?"

(TAG)

Preston
